QuestData.Title: The Pride of Kezan
QuestData.Description: This is ridiculous! Those gnomes just don't know when to stop!$B$BGoblin pride is on the line here! $n, you gotta jump into the Pride of Kezan and show them what's what!$B$BLet me know when you're ready!
QuestData.CompletionText: What are you doing back here? Get up there and shoot them down!
